</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_220" id="108v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_220_r3l17">Wilhelm von Reŷdenpuch <expan>Rıtt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_220_r3l18"> <expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her wilhelm / Eʒ hat der hochgeporen fürſt 
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / hercʒ </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_220_r3l20"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> hercʒog Stephan <expan>eıne<ex>n</ex></expan> tag 
