<del rend="strikethrough">vns vns </del> vns / <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> gnedıger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_220_r3l23">Römiſch Künig <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vvie daʒ Er ew <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab / daʒ </ab>
