<del rend="strikethrough">Alſo b </del> Vnd alſo <expan>bıte<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleıſſe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_220_r3l26">daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> dur </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_220_line_1575985531123_1483">auch </ab></add> durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> an beẏ den ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan></del> auf <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> </ab>
